---
title: Baked Veggie Korma Curry with Rapid Rice & Peanuts
description: This quickly prepped and creamy Mumbai-style curry will add the spice you never knew you needed to your night. It's filled to the brim with bright veggies, fluffy rice and finished with a sprinkling of flair from the roasted peanut and cashew mix.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
